  <name>Jigsaw Qt</name>
  <summary>A simple, casual jigsaw puzzle game</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Jigsaw Qt is a simple puzzle game for the Linux desktop. 
      It features clean image slicing, easy mouse-based controls, 
      and a responsive UI that adapts to your window size.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean piece cutout with smooth edges</li>
      <li>Simple piece snapping and clustering</li>
      <li>Natural wheel-based tray scrolling</li>
      <li>Supports custom image loading</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
